{
  "text": "Uh well uh the next session I attempt to turn more toward the heart and was attempting in this session to uh get at a point that I thought was central to the evolution of spirit, but I seem to have uh gone around. I'm sorry for that. It's sometimes very, very difficult for me to question wildly in these areas. I will just ask if there's anything that we can do to kind of put the contact or make the instrument more comfortable. Hi and you are most conscientious and the alignments are especially good. We thank you, my friends, and have been glad to speak with you. We are attempting to be of the greatest age to by taking care not to deplete this instrument. Thus, although a reserve remains, we will attempt from this working onward to keep this reserve for this instrument, has arranged its subconscious to accept this configuration I and Ra. You are all doing well, my friends. We leave you in the love and in the light of the One Infinite Creator. Go forth therefore, rejoicing and glorying in the power and in the peace of the one infinite creator A DNA.",
